the level of illumination is,

01:19:53.060 --> 01:19:56.600
a certain percentage of
these rhodopsin molecules

01:19:56.600 --> 01:19:59.250
are bleached and a certain
percentage is unbleached.

01:19:59.250 --> 01:20:01.970
